data.description:
Welcome to your urban oasis in the heart of the city! Nestled on the second floor of a charming inner-city building, this three-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment boasts contemporary laminate flooring throughout, adding a touch of modern elegance to the space.

Step into the expansive dining area, perfect for hosting gatherings with friends and family. The large eating area provides ample space for enjoying meals together, while the well-appointed kitchen offers everything you need to whip up culinary delights.

As you explore the living quarters, you'll find cozy yet efficiently designed bedrooms, each adorned with plenty of windows that flood the rooms with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. While the bedrooms and closets are of smaller size, the overall spaciousness of the apartment ensures that you'll have plenty of room to relax and unwind.

With the neighborhood on the rise, you'll be at the center of all the action, with trendy cafes, eclectic boutiques, and vibrant cultural attractions steps away. 

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stylish inner-city apartment your new home sweet home!

Owners pay a water bill; tenant pays both gas and electric services.
Off-street parking.
